main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Roddington, Newfoundland on August 19, 1959.
interesting points: The object was reported to be moving in an easterly direction., The informant identified the object as possibly being a balloon., There were insufficient data to provide a concrete identification of the object., The observation was visually confirmed from the ground., The report includes technical teletype information related to the sighting.
witness description: informant willing to provide information on the sighting
